            "text": "In practice, use form-data for file uploads. The response includes extracted text, bounding boxes, and confidence scores. To minimize latency, avoid unnecessary options like table extraction if not needed, as they add processing overhead. Profile each stage using distributed tracing tools like Jaeger to pinpoint delays."
